{"tid":1815080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台Uber Eats接單見香港地址 外賣員超崩潰　港網民：想點牛肉麵","createTime":"2020-01-07T09:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T11:16:11.000Z","uid":209657,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"67e9b20376777042a1be229a6ed3a28d959d8696","tid":1815080,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"用外賣平台下單買餐逐漸盛行，但服務範圍有地區局限，Uber Eats台灣一名外賣員近日在facebook發文，稱首次遇到落單客人竟不在台灣，而是遠在香港的尖沙咀。香港跟台灣飛機航程約1小時，連同清關及兩地巿內交通，相信就算肯「遠近送到」都最少需時4小時。帖文引來不少台港網民留言，有港人更開玩笑地留言點餐：「可以點牛肉麵嗎？」又着樓主向公司申請來回機票和住宿，一於把餐點送到香港，完成「使命必達」的服務。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3807377/org/4817f73aa1fa4bbf5ecbf2a463229bd4.jpg/T5wHLU0fL0CUfTTRudb4CBHTQETujQTzPybMqD8mzKg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3807377%2Forg%2F4817f73aa1fa4bbf5ecbf2a463229bd4.jpg%2FT5wHLU0fL0CUfTTRudb4CBHTQETujQTzPybMqD8mzKg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=4df26659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該名Uber Eats外賣員在fb群組「靠北ubereats 2.0」發文，上傳一張與客人的對話截圖，指上周五（3日）晚上11時許接到訂單，由於目的地寫着台北101大樓，他慣常地與客人再確認位置，對方回答「港威酒店」的房號，但外賣員稱在Google卻查不出地址，客人再補充「廣東道13號海港城」。<br />\n<br />\n看到客人說出一個個陌生的地址，外賣員即懷疑訂單是否來自台灣以外，其後客人稱「我在香港」，原來訂單來自尖沙咀海港城港威酒店的住客，樓主不禁大為震驚，最後通知客服處理。外賣員在帖文稱「跑這麼久第一次遇到客人不在台灣的」，但幸運的是，這場「烏龍」為他帶來免費員工餐，他選擇立即下班吃宵夜。<br />\n<br />\n外賣員的經歷吸引大批香港網民留言，紛紛「點餐」要求由台灣外送到香港，「香港人表示：可以點牛肉麵嗎」、「我想點薑母鴨」、「有胡椒餅嗎」；另有人稱外賣員應將錯就錯，一於搭飛機送到香港，「機票客人出吧」、「跟客服申請來回機票、住宿」、「搭機送去啊」、「機車改裝成水上摩托車，衝啊！」<br />\n<br />\n（facebook）"},{"pid":"173560b2a74d4330bb3be9d189d7526415321a2b","tid":1815080,"uid":1425,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:03:47.000Z","msg":"殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f00d97bb860bc701a3003d673c76b203263c9ac","tid":1815080,"uid":93202,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那人嗌？"},{"pid":"16628854a622cadca56ef081dc45dd57192aab90","tid":1815080,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:05:14.000Z","msg":"無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1123eb7bbd0ac978aedab0094300aa94c65b9d7a","tid":1815080,"uid":61282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8f00d97bb860bc701a3003d673c76b203263c9ac","tid":1815080,"uid":93202,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那人嗌？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:07:14.000Z","msg":"支那狗：都是中国一部分，不用分那麼細"},{"pid":"a4335c046b57cabf776e00a73c7641dc8412fa6f","tid":1815080,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:07:21.000Z","msg":"中国人又發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb5a0937fd4af53921fa99424d93b8fb27e4cd6","tid":1815080,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:07:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cowbellubereats/photos/a.107488494062807/126191752192481/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcowbellubereats%2Fphotos%2Fa.107488494062807%2F126191752192481%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=1152307b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cowbellubereats/photos/a.107488494062807/126191752192481/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"cd30fa8fabe482dc5e0295cd4f405978b40167d2","tid":1815080,"uid":280329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"明題係支那"},{"pid":"91b8b66d9695be9c9e391bc0055ea61cf5a12ad9","tid":1815080,"uid":31200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:10:13.000Z","msg":"支那人：不是說香港台灣都是中國的嗎？"},{"pid":"921f86bc5a7a1af440eb0a16e1784641a62bfd9f","tid":1815080,"uid":209657,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score"